(92, 1, '2021-06-04 12:39:39', '2021-06-04 12:39:39', '<h3>Simple rules to keep IAL safe and fun for everyone</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>-Sign up today, create a channel and start uploading original content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Choose a category and upload up to (5)two min videos every 7 days.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Each video can be 2 mins or less.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-No celebrity videos(amateurs only) However we would like celebrities from all industries to sign up and participate by encouraging and offering feedback to guide and inspire others. PAY IT FORWARD!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Even if you dont want to share your talents, you can sign up and enjoy content from others. You can also show your appreciation by adding to your favorite creators appreciation jar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Promote yourself! Tell your family and friends to sign up, like , vote and promote your content also.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Start building a fanbase before competition rounds start.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Competition updates COMING SOON!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IAL is all about fun, creativity, passion and dream chasing. Its a community that gives people a chance to showcase their talents and to appreciate the talents of others. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>To keep our community amazing, treat your fellow Appreciators as you would like to be treated. Respect is key. Here are a few simple rules developed according to this principle. </p>\r\n\r\n<h3>No pornography</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>IAL is not for pornography or sexually explicit content. We work closely with law enforcement and we report child exploitation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>No violence, gory and harmful content</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Dont post or comment with violent, gory content or content that encourages others to do things that might cause them to get hurt or to commit specific acts of violence, especially kids. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Professional fight videos are allowed, boxing, wrestling, MMA etcNO STREET FIGHTS!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>No hate speech and bullying</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We dont support content and comment that promotes or condones violence against individuals or groups based on race or ethnic origin, religion, disability, gender, age, nationality, veteran status or sexual orientation, or whose primary purpose is inciting hatred on the basis of these core characteristics.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>No spamming, manipulation and multiple account abuse</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Everyone hates spam. Dont post large amounts of untargeted, unwanted or repetitive content and comments in order to increase views. Creating multiple accounts with overlapping uses or in order to evade the temporary or permanent ban of a separate account is not allowed.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>No deceptive content</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Dont spread wrong information. Deceptive content, comment and account may get removed depending on their severity.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>No personal and confidential information</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To protect the safety of private individuals, anything that reveals other peoples personally identifiable information (including personal social media accounts of non-public figures without the consent of the original party) is not allowed.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>No illegal activities</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Content depicting or advocating illegal activity will not be tolerated. Such acts may be reported to law enforcement and users committed these acts may be permanently banned from IAL.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>No impersonation</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You may not impersonate others (person, group or brand) on IAL in a manner that is intended to or does mislead, confuse, or deceive others.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>No copyright and trademark infringement</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Respect originality and creativity. Give credit where credit is due. We reserve the right to reclaim usernames on behalf of businesses or individuals that hold legal claim or trademark on those usernames. Accounts using business names and/or logos to mislead others may be permanently banned.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Enforcement</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a variety of ways of enforcing our rules, including, but not limited to:</p>\r\n<ul cl