(97, 1, '2021-06-04 13:19:32', '2021-06-04 13:19:32', '<h3>IAL is where you can share your talents, your story and your passion with the rest of the world.<h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>We are</h3>\r\n<p>A cutting-edge online video platform established to give undiscovered talent exposure and recognition. The rise of the internet has made viral sensations possible but it has also created a jumble of red tape for aspiring talent  to untangle if they want to make it.</p>\r\n		\r\n<h3>At IAL</h3>\r\n<p>You can demonstrate your unique talents without having to compete with how to videos, cat videos or the already-famous etc. We aim to remove as many limitations as possible that could be in the way of you pursuing your dreams and we plan to create opportunities to help make those same dreams a reality.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>IALs mission</h3>\r\n<p>Is to create a community that gives everyone the opportunity to share their talents with the world in their own unique and amazing way.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What we value:</h3> \r\n<p>Its simple- LIFE! You only live once so why not make it count? Appreciate life and chase your dreams. \r\nIf you are not doing what you love, you are wasting your time.---Billy Joel</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Push Limits</h3>\r\n<p>So often people give up on a dream before it even has a chance to manifest into something amazing. It can happen for so many reasons but two of the biggest reasons are self-doubt and self-set limits. For once remove all doubt and limits; self-set or otherwise and push pass any and everything that tells you to give up! Quitting is not an option!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Believe in yourself</h3>\r\n<p>It always seems impossible until its done.---Nelson Mandela </p>\r\n\r\n<h3> Connect with a community of fellow Appreciators </h3>\r\n<p> Be unselfish and share your talents with everyone! Start making friends, fans, followers, APPRECIATORs and become the same for someone else! </p>', 'About us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2021-11-10 04:56:53', '2021-11-10 04:56:53', '', 0, 'https://www.ial.video/?page_id=97', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(477, 1, '2021-10-27 07:19:04', '2021-10-27 07:19:04', '<h3>IAL is where you can share your talents, your story and your passion with the rest of the world.<h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>We are</h3>\r\n<p>A cutting-edge online video platform established to give undiscovered talent exposure and recognition. The rise of the internet has made viral sensations possible but it has also created a jumble of red tape for aspiring talent  to untangle if they want to make it.</p>\r\n		\r\n<h3>At IAL</h3>\r\n<p>You can demonstrate your unique talents without having to compete with how to videos, cat videos or the already-famous etc. We aim to remove as many limitations as possible that could be in the way of you pursuing your dreams and we plan to create opportunities to help make those same dreams a reality.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>IALs mission</h3>\r\n<p>Is to create a community that gives everyone the opportunity to share their talents with the world in their own unique and amazing way.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What we value:</h3> \r\n<p>Its simple- LIFE! You only live once so why not make it count? Appreciate life and chase your dreams. \r\nIf you are not doing what you love, you are wasting your time.---Billy Joel</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Push Limits</h3>\r\n<p>So often people give up on a dream before it even has a chance to manifest into something amazing. It can happen for so many reasons but two of the biggest reasons are self-doubt and self-set limits. For once remove all doubt and limits; self-set or otherwise and push pass any and everything that tells you to give up! Quitting is not an option!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Believe in yourself</h3>\r\n<p>It always seems impossible until its done.---Nelson Mandela\r\nConnect with a community of fellow Appreciators\r\nBe unselfish and share your talents with everyone! Start making friends, fans, followers, APPRECIATORs and become the same for someone else! </p>', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '97-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-27 07:19:04', '2021-10-27 0